{"tid":1044482,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得自己係極端地負面 偏激？","createTime":"2019-03-03T02:46:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T04:05:54.000Z","uid":54226,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"9f6c1fcc82f6c29cb1117605d1a207c5f941f474","tid":1044482,"uid":54226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T02:46:14.000Z","msg":"唔知由幾時開始個人變得好負面<br />\n而且個人充斥住好重既仇恨<br />\n<br />\n可能因為香港近年發生太多負面既事<br />\n當然最主要係政治既原因<br />\n我一聽到有大陸狗講蝗語就好撚燥<br />\n一出街又全部都係班低等人種<br />\n<br />\n我諗除咗戰亂地區既人民之外<br />\n香港人係亞洲數一數二咁撚慘<br />\n地方比低等人霸咗，劣幤驅逐良幣<br />\n自己既語言 文化比人消滅又乜都做唔到<br />\n支那政府全方位咁入侵我地又抵抗唔到<br />\n<br />\n種種既政治因素令我個人好撚負面<br />\n同其他唔理政治既港豬朋友講<br />\n佢哋直情覺得你on9 杞人憂天<br />\n<br />\n呢一種既負面 仇恨情緒間接令我更加難識人<br />\n本身自己個人性格已經內向，再加上極端負面<br />\n根本就連女朋友都難有<br />\n<br />\n有冇人明白我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b333436b3517a58f894c6a5e20589eb71d6855c5","tid":1044482,"uid":54226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T02:47:28.000Z","msg":"Hi"},{"pid":"438203878983abc16d607fda4c7328dee3c09430","tid":1044482,"uid":431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T02:47:49.000Z","msg":"無時無刻都想斬柒人"},{"pid":"2cd6e3a61e17a698af660dba0d1bab73b4d1e75e","tid":1044482,"uid":54226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"438203878983abc16d607fda4c7328dee3c09430","tid":1044482,"uid":431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T02:47:49.000Z","msg":"無時無刻都想斬柒人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T02:48:23.000Z","msg":"符合你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1398dea1c5db26474a94ba8840aab6c96ae5c4a0","tid":1044482,"uid":224860,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T02:49:14.000Z","msg":"Fight club 岩你"},{"pid":"a0abd835adfe605715a10e33ea5423937f88c9e4","tid":1044482,"uid":54226,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1398dea1c5db26474a94ba8840aab6c96ae5c4a0","tid":1044482,"uid"